address.streetAddress: 3 Bed 2 Bath Double Section Plan, Westwood Estates

location.fullValue: 3 Bed 2 Bath Double Section Plan, Westwood Estates

data.description:
Welcome home to this simply adorable Amherst ranch situated on a spacious fenced lot.  Relax on the front porch or use the spacious breezeway which overlooks the fenced yard as a personal retreat.  Breezeway leads to a spacious rear deck great for entertaining.
Upon entering the remodeled dwelling, the decor captures you and instantly creates the feeling of home.  The open floor plan accented with a decorative fireplace and large windows creates an amazing space for all.  The finished basement with fireplace and extra storage completes the package for this remodeled home awaiting a new owner.
